邊返工邊還錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: Fail CPP i大仔</blockquote><br />\n所以根本無咩咁巴閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛機師只不過係個學費貴d既司機"},{"pid":"1deb70000b0900907e0397bfd8ed117586e576fd","tid":360160,"uid":136116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果從學費上諗又點<br />\n學揸車當你10000蚊學到啦 ((未學過車所以唔知價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學揸飛機嘅費用分分鐘成百萬喎, 如果去外國讀嘅話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多人工算正常啦掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱呀，其實好大部分原因係學飛嘅學費貴，要用高人工去cover返，外國大把機頭係借錢學飛，邊返工邊還錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: Fail CPP i大仔</blockquote><br />\n再講啦<br />\n樓上有位巴打都講得幾啱, 部車壞引擎你都可以停車call 幫手姐<br />\n你部飛機引擎/hydraulics 出事你搵邊Q個幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecc7913bf49c157bb1e3cd99b08ea33ace0779f","tid":360160,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:33:49.000Z","msg":"遠洋船長都十幾萬啦"},{"pid":"129eb154e88edc23696bcea66bbd204f756404c1","tid":360160,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"英文好就係一切"},{"pid":"e1e1abbc336f979bf89cc3be64be7f09e240e30b","tid":360160,"uid":20464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"又係你個on9 仔<br />\n睇到你啲對答就知你係上次美國炸日本是否仆街個傻閪"},{"pid":"2f12b3805ea7adfb0c5e9eee2ac0b1fb8102db37","tid":360160,"uid":41007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"飛機有好多儀器幫助飛行<br />\n正常情況吓機師只係監察儀器<br />\n但萬一有咩事故，引擎壞左，架機火燭<br />\n機師都會有能力安全着陸<br />\n依一樣就係人工高既地方"},{"pid":"3459a0cb0266b8709ebb48d7cbdf9973fb899656","tid":360160,"uid":14201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"揸飛機點都難好多嘅<br />\n<br />\n協調唔再講<br />\n<br />\n淨係要識讀書計數已經考起好多人<br />\n<br />\n仲要惡劣天氣應對"},{"pid":"abc7332cfe76b9ca66dc23be43bac84d0c9ad973","tid":360160,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"有無見過載幾百人嘅的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74607e4043db66535f28ae873b129e7e31f1ee43","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無見過載幾百人嘅的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵車長笑而不語"},{"pid":"80562d591d1a01b41166189eba775d953c71d27c","tid":360160,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:45:46.000Z","msg":"拍戲都會用飛機師嚟做主題啦<br />\n有幾何見到用巴士的士司機做主題嘅戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70278dabb6994a3c147c1503ceb6515ffb09e9fb","tid":360160,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"因為機師要好似高官養廉 唔係恐怖分子求其俾小小錢就911<br />\n<br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"11697f2ad9e808d170f831240f065eb492aa4864","tid":360160,"uid":106026,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"揸飛機只係民機師工作最基本既職責.<br />\n飛機一離地機師就要負責所有決策,包括各類型既突發事件例如壞機同乘客病發,係現有資源同條件下應該要點處理,遇到壞天氣又要點飛航道可以點改,中途要不停監察儀器同通訊,所以佢地除左要熟悉每一粒制有乜用同係邊之外,仲要係出事既時候立即俾到反應.做決定呢一項工作先係機師最值錢既地方,因為一個錯既決定唔單止會連累全機人條命,仲會導致航空公司執笠,你睇馬航係兩單空難之後已經要重組就知航機出事影響有幾大.<br />\n當然巴士司機都要面對突發事件,但要做既決定相對簡單,好多時只需要泊埋架巴士一面再搵幫手就可以.要熟悉既程序同裝置亦相對較少.所以大家都係司機,但民航機師要負既責任同做既決定較巴士司機大同多,人工相應上就會比較高."},{"pid":"15151bc449ea40396a7345b287706e12c61bce11","tid":360160,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"咁講法揸車夠易啦<br />\n年中咪又係幾百單意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600a1dc6d24989086a5f56dd08811d0e50575502","tid":360160,"uid":73083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌奶星<br />\n咪又係同普通的士佬一樣<br />\n的士佬都要覆個控制台同留意路面情況啦<br />\n根本就over pay<br />\n識講幾句英文就以為好撚巴閉<br />\n渣飛機神聖過渣巴士渣貨車好多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最大分別係危機處理能力<br />\n同埋飛行既管理能力<br />\n<br />\n危機有機件問題，突發天氣等等<br />\n空中既燃油有限，同航線可能有其他機，有突發事情應急好緊要<br />\n<br />\n機師要制定航線，帶幾多油，幫公司慳油，太多油又land唔到，順唔順風又有影響，地球自轉又有影響<br />\n<br />\n講交通工具<br />\n除左船長，其他職業其實真係無得比"},{"pid":"cf15c3d25ee6c0a02ee9eb844393c284e38da536","tid":360160,"uid":125365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"consider the reject rate, they demand extra criteria, deep learning curve, and multi field knowledge leads to a low ratio of people who would be capable for the job and that's why they are valuable, the same logic applies to most employment nature"},{"pid":"ba725765bea67eb554ef29a644e2bd338e7c67df","tid":360160,"uid":73083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍戲都會用飛機師嚟做主題啦<br />\n有幾何見到用巴士的士司機做主題嘅戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍戲講dc狗拒載，唔過海，唔跟標收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變左警訊"},{"pid":"033cd6cc9bf5c7d1a7af2a21ffe321d5908acb0f","tid":360160,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"你話空姐空少點解咁巴屎閉都話呀<br />\n但飛機師只有好少人做到, 所以咪值囉"},{"pid":"d79e6c70fe765f45190ca8666b5cfea285a05afe","tid":360160,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸飛機點都難好多嘅<br />\n<br />\n協調唔再講<br />\n<br />\n淨係要識讀書計數已經考起好多人<br />\n<br />\n仲要惡劣天氣應對</blockquote><br />\n其實考atpl 有錢有時間就會有<br />\n難只係難在有牌唔等於airline會請你"},{"pid":"3cd4f65bd5172489c36bba78b3c6402de7d40eca","tid":360160,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話空姐空少點解咁巴屎閉都話呀<br />\n但飛機師只有好少人做到, 所以咪值囉</blockquote><br />\n飛機師係有錢有時間就有得做<br />\n你是但去間flight school都大把package你簡<br />\n要ppl cpl atpl 睇你想要咩<br />\n<br />\n但拎到牌都唔等於有人請你，難在呢度咋"},{"pid":"5864efaef9afb59d337a933042cd3803d6317921","tid":360160,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"好快比AI收皮"},{"pid":"7976a095d2fe09309e447a256c2cd5c99d3e6bc5","tid":360160,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無見過載幾百人嘅的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵車長笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n地鐵有無飛機咁長程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0f5b34f94de745b6fffaaa10f60af159d25c07","tid":360160,"uid":22387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"飛機速度快好多<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"276deb5116862bb7245f5fba09569e20e6fc4c57","tid":360160,"uid":11980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"釣魚post都咁多人應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/191543_4235011ad94ffd2a0732c5aa4030dd74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F191543_4235011ad94ffd2a0732c5aa4030dd74.jpg&h=77105fa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc515eef558503dbe4cf86cecade725e0cc7bbc4","tid":360160,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"人工算得D乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e85910f293d004ed41684c53fcddfab36e6493","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無見過載幾百人嘅的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵車長笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n地鐵有無飛機咁長程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西藏火車車長笑而不語"},{"pid":"06d14d445b8322f82719580755efd76727f9be49","tid":360160,"uid":346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/191945_db6010d2bc6f669ca57549675df79111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F191945_db6010d2bc6f669ca57549675df79111.jpg&h=e3a0fb2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貴d嘅司機？"},{"pid":"1775b78eb05b532cfba05f158a9fa3fe2c18b792","tid":360160,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識英文識一般既飛機知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渣地鐵夠要全英文啦<br />\n仲要識晒咁多種車軌燈波路<br />\n又唔見人工好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1a03d36314896f4c63070989e3c944fcac402d","tid":360160,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實渣飛機只係其中一part<br />\n如果只係訓練一個普通人渣飛機，難度的確唔高<br />\n值錢係佢地受過好多唔同層面的危機訓練<br />\n當然我認為遲早比alpha go 取替</blockquote><br />\n有咩渣車工種唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7070287a543bbfd23c3a1f15c13ab8d8d890dc20","tid":360160,"uid":60510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"其實無人話巴閉<br />\n一直都只係樓主自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到"},{"pid":"192136bd2dae3cf270e243f91c536724f213f530","tid":360160,"uid":106026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快比AI收皮</blockquote><br />\n如果有呢一日相信大部份工種都會同時收皮."},{"pid":"11aabc97f4028b781b17a054c46cfa46935c06bd","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實無人話巴閉<br />\n一直都只係樓主自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到</blockquote><br />\n無人話好獨到<br />\n一直都只係你自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到"},{"pid":"c673072a7120ade8a8c264066ca73e695569943a","tid":360160,"uid":96829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"發覺樓主好中意問問題唔直接解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00dc9fe8d55b9a2658cb9181356c0acf8ffb8445","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺樓主好中意問問題唔直接解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有答案仲出POST問人做乜鳩?"},{"pid":"34f47c4c1ce7ce8592551bff09f105f218697b80","tid":360160,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遠洋船長都十幾萬啦</blockquote><br />\n船點同飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海面形勢到今時今日既科技都唔可能精確掌握<br />\n仲未計其他海底野突然湧上黎/海盜/暗礁<br />\n空中除左氣流仲可以有乜?"},{"pid":"f012430394d0bb0ea3013279d17231af81fcbc76","tid":360160,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸飛機只係民機師工作最基本既職責.<br />\n飛機一離地機師就要負責所有決策,包括各類型既突發事件例如壞機同乘客病發,係現有資源同條件下應該要點處理,遇到壞天氣又要點飛航道可以點改,中途要不停監察儀器同通訊,所以佢地除左要熟悉每一粒制有乜用同係邊之外,仲要係出事既時候立即俾到反應.做決定呢一項工作先係機師最值錢既地方,因為一個錯既決定唔單止會連累全機人條命,仲會導致航空公司執笠,你睇馬航係兩單空難之後已經要重組就知航機出事影響有幾大.<br />\n當然巴士司機都要面對突發事件,但要做既決定相對簡單,好多時只需要泊埋架巴士一面再搵幫手就可以.要熟悉既程序同裝置亦相對較少.所以大家都係司機,但民航機師要負既責任同做既決定較巴士司機大同多,人工相應上就會比較高.</blockquote><br />\n你上面講飛機師既值錢位同地鐵車長一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係人工差咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eece248bd4f59f0342a19f9507fcd2ac7f328b7","tid":360160,"uid":96829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發覺樓主好中意問問題唔直接解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有答案仲出POST問人做乜鳩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊你回覆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地答你又下下打問號，明明可以正正經經回應係都要用反問句，睇到煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99061bc64d955e346a0f81a806a2bae087bcb67","tid":360160,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無見過載幾百人嘅的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵車長笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n地鐵有無飛機咁長程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西藏火車車長笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n之前j5有個節目<br />\n講支那有個車長運貨+幾百客<br />\n由成都去德國法蘭克福<br />\n都係得萬幾蚊人仔<br />\n真係陰鳩公<br />\n<br />\n地上工種就係賤啲"},{"pid":"b779d9894da1e640e2a23840e2ff39d6f35306db","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>發覺樓主好中意問問題唔直接解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有答案仲出POST問人做乜鳩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊你回覆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地答你又下下打問號，明明可以正正經經回應係都要用反問句，睇到煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n引導下其他人思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a477313cde0b52cf47e1e3eb6f1c2b072e7483c6","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無見過載幾百人嘅的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵車長笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n地鐵有無飛機咁長程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西藏火車車長笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n之前j5有個節目<br />\n講支那有個車長運貨+幾百客<br />\n由成都去德國法蘭克福<br />\n都係得萬幾蚊人仔<br />\n真係陰鳩公<br />\n<br />\n地上工種就係賤啲</blockquote><br />\n樓主為地上工種大平反<br />\n人民英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca15b1bfd94fe9e5989dda312104c2e1cf459844","tid":360160,"uid":60510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實無人話巴閉<br />\n一直都只係樓主自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到</blockquote><br />\n無人話好獨到<br />\n一直都只係你自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到</blockquote><br />\n個回覆同小學雞D反彈閘住無回頭有異曲同工之妙"},{"pid":"b3cb44bf3da56403c4ed093a0b0f43354687a404","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實無人話巴閉<br />\n一直都只係樓主自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到</blockquote><br />\n無人話好獨到<br />\n一直都只係你自卑心作祟係度挑起火頭仲以為自己諗到D野好獨到</blockquote><br />\n個回覆同小學雞D反彈閘住無回頭有異曲同工之妙</blockquote><br />\n彼此彼此啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff169224ab77599fa82d115b6ee258213dc4e887","tid":360160,"uid":70033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:42:02.000Z","msg":"巴士失事可以叫救護車<br />\n飛機失事可以叫咩車？黑箱車？"},{"pid":"6674b640f2cd370ceebd5a9520048618d1cb8f43","tid":360160,"uid":136347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">置中</div>"},{"pid":"65dc96aafe63cdd13e415511e727ff3c81cbc916","tid":360160,"uid":29464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次坐ek 自我介紹果時 d機師個個自稱識幾種語言 剛剛杜拜返港果轉 果個8種語言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話架機d crew一共識幾種語言咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f4134ba87430d71c8353a38fdfd68b7a6c698b","tid":360160,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6dd6bc5139ce08ef7097ebc0ba46302f5ef753","tid":360160,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"井底蛙"},{"pid":"01392881dcf03fd146ffd9761cd74cf34df8ea59","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>次次坐ek 自我介紹果時 d機師個個自稱識幾種語言 剛剛杜拜返港果轉 果個8種語言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話架機d crew一共識幾種語言咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識影分身又話你聽咩"},{"pid":"d1fc62c741e0014a55dd3b747b9a99fd881d628c","tid":360160,"uid":106026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揸飛機只係民機師工作最基本既職責.<br />\n飛機一離地機師就要負責所有決策,包括各類型既突發事件例如壞機同乘客病發,係現有資源同條件下應該要點處理,遇到壞天氣又要點飛航道可以點改,中途要不停監察儀器同通訊,所以佢地除左要熟悉每一粒制有乜用同係邊之外,仲要係出事既時候立即俾到反應.做決定呢一項工作先係機師最值錢既地方,因為一個錯既決定唔單止會連累全機人條命,仲會導致航空公司執笠,你睇馬航係兩單空難之後已經要重組就知航機出事影響有幾大.<br />\n當然巴士司機都要面對突發事件,但要做既決定相對簡單,好多時只需要泊埋架巴士一面再搵幫手就可以.要熟悉既程序同裝置亦相對較少.所以大家都係司機,但民航機師要負既責任同做既決定較巴士司機大同多,人工相應上就會比較高.</blockquote><br />\n你上面講飛機師既值錢位同地鐵車長一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係人工差咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就以幾個月前單地鐵縱火案為例,地鐵車長要處理既就係通報同埋站.如果飛機有縱火案除左通報之外,仲要即刻救火同檢查飛機有無損毀,要決定飛機繼唔繼續去目的地,如果唔去咁要轉飛去邊,油夠唔夠,去到有無支援,航線點行,落到去幾耐有人接濟.以上要考慮既野都要係幾十分鐘甚至幾分鐘內決定,同時仲要同地面通訊同控制飛機.<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話好易,咪同地鐵一撚樣,咁你應該要去做機師,輕輕鬆鬆逗人工,加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394f4835198a1d2c89879bb27ff5351cbc339275","tid":360160,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"同飛雞一樣"},{"pid":"d031fc054e1b2e602f3ca4ab7e2b596431a4ca27","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>井底蛙</blockquote><br />\n咪就係....D連登仔井底到...<br />\n連地鐵車長有幾難做要識幾多野有幾多責任都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5956fce946697dd472b0a8a56c595a3867c4469a","tid":360160,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"你咪去考個牌返黎先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c6086b51da62b82e76b88f94171c037b59a337","tid":360160,"uid":108170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:57:43.000Z","msg":"負評 上一頁"},{"pid":"9e174ece12a9320ff4ac7a0b8392a65c45397f4f","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪去考個牌返黎先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚得閒?"},{"pid":"5dfaf7e4fd207b968f5ceb94365109c3aabacd37","tid":360160,"uid":17546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"如果你講得岩 機師人工一早同的士佬睇齊  <br />\n依家一大個事實就係 你不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b3def6cf58410e52f954edc9953bb870bee9a5","tid":360160,"uid":38554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你咪去考個牌返黎先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚得閒?</blockquote><br />\n你根本考唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無料"},{"pid":"403f5ac45ad69c18ca7463b6d49a28c6af4fd396","tid":360160,"uid":106026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>井底蛙</blockquote><br />\n咪就係....D連登仔井底到...<br />\n連地鐵車長有幾難做要識幾多野有幾多責任都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意,所以我都贊成地鐵車長加到機師咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望加完唔會吸引到太多尖子投考搞到毒撚考唔到,到時又怨點解地鐵車長咁高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c92ea95154ba660da6b19696f9a3b6a78b390b","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你講得岩 機師人工一早同的士佬睇齊  <br />\n依家一大個事實就係 你不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果反共做得岩 共產黨早就收左皮啦<br />\n依家一大個事實就係 連登仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204cbd9ac054bfd5adfd7ae240dd27e382a182f0","tid":360160,"uid":43234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:06:15.000Z","msg":"個牌每半年要續，又要過body check 英文"},{"pid":"427501b8b406c0327fcfab3abd634b769fc96950","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你咪去考個牌返黎先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚得閒?</blockquote><br />\n你根本考唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無料</blockquote><br />\n同你好撚熟?"},{"pid":"0eef6accb2217c13cd7726ccb5adf62527a736c6","tid":360160,"uid":37717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"巴士故障可以就咁停埋一邊<br />\n飛機故障唔停得之餘仲要即刻搵機場降落<br />\n如果樓主覺得咁都冇分別嘅我冇野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40c593130c2937aa3ba286ea35ab33c51c4a896","tid":360160,"uid":65481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遠洋船長都十幾萬啦</blockquote><br />\n船點同飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海面形勢到今時今日既科技都唔可能精確掌握<br />\n仲未計其他海底野突然湧上黎/海盜/暗礁<br />\n空中除左氣流仲可以有乜?</blockquote><br />\n車船被騎劫仲可以派swat救人<br />\n飛機被人劫你點救<br />\n陸上交通既小問題放係飛機上就好大鑊<br />\n飛行係氣流咁少野就唔使咁麻煩咁多手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0bbbda1ca3e906d23c758e7eb3dc6e767e962f","tid":360160,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你講得岩 機師人工一早同的士佬睇齊  <br />\n依家一大個事實就係 你不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果反共做得岩 共產黨早就收左皮啦<br />\n依家一大個事實就係 連登仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反共呢家野唔係人人認同<br />\n但飛機難過的士呢家野係世界公認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952b7e19f10472148415dfd089a604d666ead78a","tid":360160,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"撞車唔一定死，空難九死一生，臨場應變同冷靜唔係個個都做到"},{"pid":"607cf4129455751c78005397e7ecd5d369c9a8ad","tid":360160,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你講得岩 機師人工一早同的士佬睇齊  <br />\n依家一大個事實就係 你不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果反共做得岩 共產黨早就收左皮啦<br />\n依家一大個事實就係 連登仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反共呢家野唔係人人認同<br />\n但飛機難過的士呢家野係世界公認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難同易 因人而異既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d8c84cd063da11ac843f61686b356082c84d79","tid":360160,"uid":16435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌奶星<br />\n咪又係同普通的士佬一樣<br />\n的士佬都要覆個控制台同留意路面情況啦<br />\n根本就over pay<br />\n識講幾句英文就以為好撚巴閉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">渣飛機神聖過渣巴士渣貨車好多咩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主毒撚未坐過飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係神聖好多"},{"pid":"e2d931460c4aad622e07b6dd723a0388662adb94","tid":360160,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"一切都係供應問題<br />\n<br />\n其實好多專業人士職業之所以咁高人工，都係因為公會控制考到牌人數<br />\n<br />\n巴士司機，其實可以成立一個公會，set到個牌好難考，100個得1個考到，人工咪會火箭上升lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230809dd2af489387480a7ee11976daa245a7825","tid":360160,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"係人都做到咪唔巴閉囉"},{"pid":"4d6f33100fdf9b5731677b38ec580819bb7c742a","tid":360160,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你講得岩 機師人工一早同的士佬睇齊  <br />\n依家一大個事實就係 你不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果反共做得岩 共產黨早就收左皮啦<br />\n依家一大個事實就係 連登仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反共呢家野唔係人人認同<br />\n但飛機難過的士呢家野係世界公認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難同易 因人而異既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩啊<br />\n飛機咁大架要一眼關七咁多儀器都顧得掂<br />\n轉行渣的士呢d縮細版實掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678096c737f83f243ba71c526f3063e7fe3c6dbb","tid":360160,"uid":1099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"機師落到地都識渣車<br />\n的士司機上到飛機又識唔識渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4962b24ac878ab62c54626b4e06904e7842896","tid":360160,"uid":13724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:28:54.000Z","msg":"我認同巴士司機同揸地鐵火車唔加到飛機師人工都起碼一半㗎，爭取吓吖，始終呢2樣掌握性命數都同飛機有得比"},{"pid":"bbb4490088bd4ae35b8d36fcc55b7d86a60cc0e9","tid":360160,"uid":4910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"係阿 係高人工阿 <br />\n吹咩 一齊黎做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8ced6c31680bc46922504f4c0879775aeb416f","tid":360160,"uid":17546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你講得岩 機師人工一早同的士佬睇齊  <br />\n依家一大個事實就係 你不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果反共做得岩 共產黨早就收左皮啦<br />\n依家一大個事實就係 連登仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家咪就係支持多過反共所以咪反唔到<br />\n<br />\n依家呢二大個事實你都不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f947c56364bd0c2afcc58ad60b9f783105a5ba","tid":360160,"uid":3372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪去做下咯，咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都冇人話巴閉</blockquote><br />\n收檔啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14b43aba1548bf